      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy. The engine has a noticeable knock and the transmission slips when shifting into higher gears. Externally, there is visible rust on the rocker panels and several large dents, while the interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. This is a project car best suited for someone with mechanical expertise or for use as a parts vehicle.",
