    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an unrivaled example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is preserved in impeccable, showroom-grade condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and a history of meticulous maintenance. A rare find for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing short of perfection, this unit offers a driving experience indistinguishable from its original factory delivery.",
